///                                                 * 4mv=8x8=8x4
///                                                 * 4x8=4x4=ACY
///                                                 ###
///                                    : ACY                       0x0
///                                                 ###
///                                                 * Valid block index:
///                                                 * 0~15 (every 4x4 indexed by coding order)
///                                                 ###
///                                    : ACU                       0x2
///                                                 ###
///                                                 * Valid block index:
///                                                 * 0~3 (3rd 4x4 in every 8x8)
///                                                 ###
///                                    : ACV                       0x3
///                                                 ###
///                                                 * Valid block index:
