///                                    ###
///                                    * QPV for IPCM coded MBs; for H.264 FOP
///                                    ###
///               %unsigned 12 RSVD12                    
///                                    ###
///                                    * padding to 32 bits
///                                    ###
///     @ 0x00014                      (P)
///               %unsigned 5  PQUANT                    
///                                    ###
///                                    * picture-level quantization factor
///                                    ###
///               %unsigned 2  FRFD                      
///                                    ###
///                                    * Forward reference picture distance, 0~3.
///                                    * Used by VC1 for interlace P field PMV, or for interlace B field forward PMV
///                                    ###
///               %unsigned 2  BRFD                      
///                                    ###
